import React from "react"; const ViewCustomer = (props: any) => { const { details } = props; return (
{details && (
Name
{details.name}
Email
{details.email}
Phone
{details.phone}
Address
{details.address}
Status
{details.status}
Landlord
{details.landlord}
Payment
{details.paymentType}
)}
); }; export default ViewCustomer;
